INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('6054','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-align: center;\">产品简介</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&ldquo;Cimory西莫尼&rdquo;是印度尼西亚著名食品品牌，荷兰&ldquo;Makro万客隆&rdquo;集团的子公司之一，由印尼华侨创立于2006年，专注于高端乳制品行业，致力于用新鲜牛奶和澳洲奶粉生产高营养乳制品。与荷兰&ldquo;Makro万客隆&rdquo;集团合作的，采用的国际最新技术&mdash;&mdash;UHT(巴氏杀菌)制造设备和无菌灌装生产线。&ldquo;Cimory西莫尼&rdquo;的产品很丰富，有酸奶、鲜奶、酸奶饮料、饼干，巧克力、冰淇淋等等，是唯一一家在能在印尼生产新鲜天然干酪的公司。其产品不仅在印尼50000多家超市销售，占印尼80%以上的市场份额，更是远销新加坡、马来西亚、菲律宾等地。西莫尼公司是一个涉及多个行业的集团公司，从食品机械制造，到乳制品生产，再到目前，仅在雅加达就有20多家的大型&ldquo;西莫尼&rdquo;连锁游乐休闲美食购物中心，&ldquo;Cimory西莫尼&rdquo;在印尼家喻户晓，口碑极好</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">产品卖点</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">西莫尼酸奶是高端奶：中国人的钠摄入量过高，高钠摄入导致血压升高，而高血压是心脏病和中风的主要诱发因素。中风和心脏病分别是中国第二大及第三大死亡原因。所以毎个人都知道要吃清淡一点，少放盐，为的就是减少钠的吸收，也就是说食物中的钠越少越好，但脂肪含量难道是越高越好吗？西莫尼酸奶之所是高端，因为她做到了钠和脂肪含量是其他品牌的一半！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 酸奶配料简单，不添加任何化学添加剂和使用欧洲最新技术&mdash;&mdash;UHT(巴氏杀菌)制造设备及无菌灌装生产线生产的常温酸奶,保质期比国内同类产品长出2-3个月，公司致力于用新鲜牛奶和澳洲奶粉生产高营养乳制品，酸奶已经成为健康饮品的代名词，喜欢喝酸奶的人越来越多，但很多人去超市挑选的时候，仍然存在误区，比如，认为酸奶越浓稠，质量就越好。其实酸奶的稠度与营养价值并无直接关系，您在选购的时候，应当更加注重包装上标明的蛋白质、钠、脂肪的含量。通常，酸奶的蛋白质含量在2.3%以上，若低于此数值，便不能被称为酸奶，脂肪的含量当然是越低越好。市场上还有很多口味酸甜的乳酸饮料，与酸奶不属于一类产品，蛋白质含量仅为1%以上，营养价值远低于酸奶。很多市售的酸奶为了让稠度增加，制作当中需要加入多种增稠剂如明胶或膳食纤维类物质，西莫尼酸奶比国内酸奶稀一些，但口感更好，特别是年轻人和儿童十分喜欢。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-